---
import SectionStructure from '../../structures/SectionStructure.astro';
---

<SectionStructure idSection="testimonials" sectionClasses="bg-[#F2F2F2]" wrapperClasses="py-20 min-h-[250px] justify-center">
  <article class="flex flex-col gap-5 justify-center items-center">
    <div class="flex justify-center w-full bg-blue-100 items-center relative">
      <img src="/public/assets/testimonial/bg.png" class="absolute max-h-[400px] -z-30" alt="" />
      <video autoplay loop muted controls src="/public/assets/testimonial/testimonial.mp4" class="w-[80%] object-contain rounded-[10px]"></video>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white shadow-lg flex rounded-[10px] pb-8 flex-col gap-3 p-3">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl">Dr. Mads Gilber</h3>
      <p class="text-sm font-medium">
        Mads Gilbert is a Norwegian emergency medicine specialist who has made frequent trips to Palestinian refugee camps in Lebanon, the West Bank and Gaza since 1982.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-medium">The Israeli government has permanently banned him from entering the Gaza Strip. “They forbid us to be there with them… but they can’t forbid us to help them!”</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</SectionStructure>
